g.text: Alice's Private Transfer to Bob without ZWToken Awareness
Alice1 Wraps Token into ZWToken and Burns It
Generate a provable burn address (e.g., using Poseidon hash)
mint amount ZWToken to provable burn address
emit CommitmentUpdated(commitment, to=provable burn address, amount)
emit Deposited(from=Alice1, to=provable burn address, amount)
Alice1 does not hold ZWToken and is unaware of ZWToken
Alice1 Generates Proof of Provable Burn Address for Reminting
Alice2 / Relayer Remints and Unwraps Underlying Token to Bob
ZWToken.remint(proof, commitment, nullifier, to=Bob, amount, withdrawUnderlying=true)
Bob does not hold ZWToken and is unaware of ZWToken
